title: Pita Jungle
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Part of chain restaurant in the Southwest, offering Middle Eastern and Mediterranean food. Has vegan suitable items, including a few appetizers, sides, and salads; the falafel pita, veggie wrap, and macro plate. See website chart which notes which items are vegan. Casual sit-down dining. Relocated from 1250 E Apache Blvd.
